Travelers OnLine
    
Wednesday, November 13, 2002
    
Google, Inc.
[Private]
Mountain View CA 94043
phone: [Private]
fax: ([Private]
    
re: Legal Department - message removal
    
Please remove the following message ID's from the Google 
Groups search engine,archives, hard drives, computers, caches, or like storage devices.
    
These items were posted by our company or through our company and are considered copyrighted material owned by our company whereas no permission has been provided to Google or its affiliates for any of the above purposes.

If you prefer an ASCII transmission of the following message ID's you may email or fax the appropriate email address in which to address the ASCII file. [Private], [Private]
    
                                          Sincerely,
